Description: 
    Employee vacation balance record

Supported Commands:
    help
        Print this help message.

    add-record
        Add new employee to the vacation record.

    rem-record
        Remove employee from record.

    request-leave
        Send leave request (Annual - sick - unpaid).
    
    print-record
        Display the entire company vacation record.
    
    my-record
        Display your record.
    
    vacations
        Display public holidays.
    
    quit
        Exit program.
------------------------------------------------------------
